e="preserve">The Mürzzuschlag District is a former district in the state of Styria in Austria. Mürzzuschlag merged with the district of Bruck an der Mur to form the new district of Bruck-Mürzzuschlag on 1 January 2013.
Municipalities.
Suburbs, hamlets and other subdivisions of a municipality are indicated in small characters.
